Package: ComplexMap
Title: A Toolset for the Functional Analysis and Interactive Visualization of Protein Complex Data
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2026-02-18
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Qingzhou",
           family = "Zhang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "zqzneptune@hotmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9540-2624"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive workflow for the quality control,
    refinement, functional enrichment, and network-based analysis of protein
    complex datasets. ComplexMap allows for the quantitative evaluation of
    predicted complexes against a reference and provides an interactive
    Cytoscape.js-powered Shiny explorer to navigate the functional landscape
    of a protein complex map.
URL: https://zqzneptune.github.io/ComplexMap, https://github.com/zqzneptune/ComplexMap
